CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 24, 2011

[Cite as 05/24/2011 Case Announcements #2, 2011-Ohio-2471.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2011-0281. Disciplinary Counsel v. Cantrell.

This cause is scheduled for oral argument on Tuesday, May 24, 2011. Upon consideration of respondent’s motion for continuance of oral argument, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
